==Behind the scenes==
"[[Wikipedia:Halcyon|Halcyon]]" is an old-English name for a species of colorful diving bird, known today as a "[[Wikipedia:kingfisher|kingfisher]]." Halcyon is also a synonym for peace or peaceful. In connection to this, the phrase "halcyon days" is often used to refer to a bygone time of happiness and contentment.

